body:
I would like to take on some files, but slightly unclear on what to do. For instance, in liballoc/boxed.rs:

```
#[stable(feature = "rust1", since = "1.0.0")]
impl<I: Iterator + ?Sized> Iterator for Box<I> {
    type Item = I::Item;
    fn next(&mut self) -> Option<I::Item> { (**self).next() }
    fn size_hint(&self) -> (usize, Option<usize>) { (**self).size_hint() }
}
```

Where would I implement Send/Sync? I'm looking at #22715 for examples/guidance but not getting much out of it. Once I can do that single file, it would be my pleasure to work on the libcore files as well.
